His father is said to be {{ill|Hikozaka no Ō|ja|日子坐王|12=draft|12=draft}}, a prince of [[Kōka Tennō]], and his mother is {{ill|Okitsu Nagamizu Yorihime|ja|息長水依比売|12=draft|12=draft}}, the daughter of {{ill|Amenokage no Mikoto|ja|天御影命|12=draft|12=draft}}. He is believed to have had siblings, including {{ill|Mizuho no Mawaka no Ō|ja|水穂真若王|12=draft|12=draft}}, the ancestor of the [[Ankoku no Miyatsuko]], and {{ill|Mizuho no Iyo Yorihime|ja|水穂五百依比売|12=draft|12=draft}}, as well as {{ill|Mii no Tsuhime|ja|御井津比売|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, the chronology described in the ''Kuni no Miyatsuko Hongi'' conflicts with the genealogical records in the ''Kojiki.''

